@DonAgalloch

I would highly recommend Mass Effect 2 if you enjoyed Chrono Trigger.  ME2 might have a pretty large shooting structure to it being a third person action/adventure/shooter, but it has remarkable depth in character development.  You can also have a big impact on the storyline a la Chrono Trigger, though not nearly as much as time travel of course ; )

Seriously, give it a shot.  It's not a classic like this, but it is a wonderfully crafted game.
